# Spartan Environment Setup

## Virtual Environment Activation
Always run the following command from the root level before executing any terminal commands:

```bash
source search-and-personalisation-snp/spartan-env/bin/activate
```

This activates the `spartan-env` virtual environment to ensure commands run with the correct dependencies and configurations.

## Critical Rules
- ✅ Always activate the virtual environment before running Python scripts
- ✅ Always activate the virtual environment before installing packages
- ✅ Always activate the virtual environment before running tests
